rel_cont_id: E2028.NC.SKQ23-12S | E2029.NC.SKQ23-12S | E2030.NC.SKQ23-12S | Larson NC1 | Larson NC2 | Larson NC3 | Larson NC4 | Larson NC5
geo_loc_name_method: Obtained using the decimalLatitude and decimalLongitude coordinates to look up in the International Hydrographic Organization (IHO) geospatial World_Seas_IHO_v3 dataset.

If not specified in the corresponding method field, then the field was measured.
altitude_method: Calculated by subtracting the maximumDepthInMeters from the tot_depth_water_col.

samp_store_method_additional: Stored in a 1 L brown Nalgene bottle
samp_mat_process: Water samples were collected from the niskin into 1 L bottles then filtered through a 0.22 micron sterivex filter using a peristaltic pump with tubing attached to the outlet end of the sterivex.
prep_method_additional: 2 mL of 96% molecular grade ethanol used for preservation.
nucl_acid_ext_kit: Qiagen DNeasy Blood and Tissue Kit
nucl_acid_ext_modify: Modified for sterivex, reagent volume altered
concentration_method: Qubit Fluorometer v.4 dsDNA high sensitivity kit
nucl_acid_ext_method_additional: Extractions completed in a Biosafety Cabinet for sterility purposes.
tot_depth_water_col_method: Looked up in the GEBCO 2024 bathymetric dataset using the decimalLatitude and decimalLongitude coordinates.
measurements_from: Most environmental metadata measurements reported for this sample are taken from the primary sensor from the bottle file, with the exception of chlorophyll, silicate, ammonium, phosphate, nitrate, nitrite, and PAR where the CTD measurement was taken. geo_loc_name, altitude, and tot_depth_water_col were calculated using the methods described in the field's corresponding method field. If not specified in the corresponding method field, then the field was measured.
altitude_method: Calculated by subtracting the maximumDepthInMeters from the tot_depth_water_col.
